maintext:
HARRISBURG, Pa. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday evening’s drawing of the Pennsylvania Lottery’s “Pick 3 Evening” game were:
2-0-2, Wild: 8
(two, zero, two; Wild: eight)
